### Test 59: Search Series VO Sources
### GET /MediaSource/series/vo
### Parameters: mediaId, imdbId, title, seasonNumber, episodeNumber
GET {{baseUrl}}/MediaSource/series/vo?mediaId=1399&imdbId=tt0903747&title=Breaking%20Bad&seasonNumber=1&episodeNumber=1
Accept: application/json

### Test 60: Search Series VF Sources
### GET /MediaSource/series/vf
### Parameters: mediaId, title, seasonNumber, episodeNumber
GET {{baseUrl}}/MediaSource/series/vf?mediaId=1399&title=Breaking%20Bad&seasonNumber=1&episodeNumber=1
Accept: application/json


### Notes for MediaSource Controller:
### - VF = French version (Version Fran√ßaise)
### - VO = Original version (Version Originale)
### - mediaId: The internal media identifier
### - imdbId: IMDB identifier (only for VO series searches)
### - title: Movie or series title
### - year: Release year (only for movies)
### - seasonNumber: Season number (only for series)
### - episodeNumber: Episode number (only for series)

